{"lemma":"فاحِشَةٍ","slug":"فاحِشَةٍ","root":"ف.ح.ش","root_slug":"ف-ح-ش","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ح-ش","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فاحِشَة","root":"فحش","pos":"N","occurrence_count":17},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33122","n33129"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%90%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"obscenity, immorality","tags":["countable"],"examples":[{"text":"وَلَا تَقْرَبُوا الزِّنَى ۖ إِنَّهُ كَانَ فَاحِشَةً وَسَاءَ سَبِيلًا","english":"And do not go near adultery for it is an obscenity and a hazardous path"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the feminine form of active participle of the verb فَحَشَ (faḥaša)."},"ipa":["/faː.ħi.ʃa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33122","headword_ar":"فاحشهُ","root":"fH$","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b*A^","text_ar":"بذا"},{"kind":"text","text":",) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufaAHa$ahN","text_ar":"مُفَاحَشَهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T and K in that art.,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He vied with him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strove to surpass him, in foul, unseemly, gross,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obscene, speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"language:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he held such discourse with him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the inf. n. is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mubaA*aA^apN","text_ar":"مُبَاذَاَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T and K in that art.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n33129","headword_ar":"فَاحِشَةٌ","root":"fH$","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An excess; an enormity; anything exceeding the bounds of rectitude:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing excessively, enormously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beyond measure, foul, evil, bad, abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unseemly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gross, immodest, lewd,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obscene:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything not agreeable with truth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crime, that is very foul, evil, bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything forbidden by God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"action, that is foul, evil, bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHo$aA='u","text_ar":"فَحْشَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAHi$apN","text_ar":"فَاحِشَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an enormity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excessive sin, beyond measure foul, evil, bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that reason disapproves, and the law regards as foul, evil, bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (Bd in ii. 164:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAHi$apN","text_ar":"فَاحِشَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fawaAHi$u","text_ar":"فَوَاحِشُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, TA.) Also, particularly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Adultery,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fornication;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHo$aA='u","text_ar":"فَحْشَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Bd in xii. 24; &c.:) so in the Kur iv. 23 and lxv. 1 [as well as in numerous other instances]: or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fAH$p","text_ar":"فاحشة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or excess] there mentioned is the women's going out without permission: (Mgh, Msb:) or their using foul language against their husband's relations, by reason of the sharpness of their tongues. (Esh-Sháfi'ee.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHo$aA='u","text_ar":"فَحْشَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"particularly signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Niggardliness, tenaciousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avarice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the payment of the poor-rate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abstaining"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altogether"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from paying it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) So in the Kur ii. 271. (A, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Lth","K","TA","Msb","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}